responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "1379CAE44C9C10D35FBC699FA9A6ABD3", "That would be most excellent. You could do no better than to aid a man of my high esteem. You may look upon the diary and notice also the missing pages. Salvagers and looters have spread rumors that they flutter within. ")
